cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper involves computer vision (CV) techniques for 3D scene reconstruction and inpainting, which suggests cs.CV as the most likely sub-category. The use of deep reinforcement learning (RL) also suggests cs.AI as a likely sub-category. The paper also involves graphics (GR) techniques for point cloud integration and multi-view selection. The joint learning of all steps suggests a focus on machine learning (LG) and robotics (RO) techniques.
